          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1708528753331-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is golden, remove the pan from the heat and add<strong> </strong>the <strong>BBQ sauce</strong></p><p>Return the pan to a medium-high heat, cover with a lid and cook for a further 10-12 min, stirring occasionally, until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>smoky BBQ chicken</strong></p>",
