    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a pot over a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced pepper</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 6-7 min or until softened (add a splash of water if the pot is looking a little dry!)</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>drained sweetcorn</strong> to the pot and cook for a further 1-2 min or until the sweetcorn is warmed through – this is your <strong>pepper & corn salad</strong></p>",
